<bibRefCitation id="EFCF4B4AFFB3EC070764FF27FA5CFF71" author="Whitehead, V. B. &amp; Steiner, K. E." box="[1123,1432,225,251]" pageId="4" pageNumber="322" pagination="143 - 277" refId="ref6735" refString="Whitehead, V. B. &amp; Steiner, K. E. (2001) Oil-collecting bees of the winter rainfall area of South Africa (Melittidae, Rediviva). Annals of the South African Museum, 108, 143 - 277." type="journal article" year="2001">Whitehead &amp; Steiner 2001</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation id="EFCF4B4AFFB3EC070390FEC3FE57FE95" author="Whitehead, V. B. &amp; Steiner, K. E. &amp; Eardley, C. D." box="[151,403,261,287]" pageId="4" pageNumber="322" pagination="122 - 141" refId="ref6780" refString="Whitehead, V. B., Steiner, K. E. &amp; Eardley, C. D. (2008) Oil-collecting bees mostly of the summer rainfall area of southern Africa (Hymenoptera: Melittidae: Rediviva). Journal of the Kansas Entomological Society, 81, 122 - 141. https: // doi. org / 10.2317 / JKES- 703.12.1" type="journal article" year="2008">
Whitehead 
<emphasis id="B92AEAA9FFB3EC070210FEC0FE94FE95" box="[279,336,261,287]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="322">et al.</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
